    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Through your heritage, you can replicate a hag's magic. Choose one common spell of 4th rank or lower from those available to a coven, including the spells contributed to a coven by a hag of your mother's type. You can cast this spell once per day as a 4th-rank occult innate spell.</p>\n<p>Spells available to all covens are Augury, Charm, Clairaudience, Clairvoyance, Dream Message, and Illusory Disguise. The eligible spells granted by the most prominent types of hag are:</p>\n<p><strong>Cuckoo Hag</strong> Nightmare, Spellwrack</p>\n<p><strong>Iron Hag</strong> Earthbind, Spellwrack</p>\n<p><strong>Sea Hag</strong> Humanoid Form, Mariner's Curse, Water Walk</p>\n<p><strong>Sweet Hag</strong> Charm, Honeyed Words, Outcast's Curse</p>"
    },
